citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:50 AM on
13-JAN-17.
The inspector arrived at the facility at approximately 10:50 AM and proceeded to the office. The office was locked
and a phone call to the number provided went unanswered. The inspector waited at the office for 30 minutes. A
business card was left at the facility.
